 originating from wildlife are oriented towards the developed world and are less useful for biodiverse, low-income economies. We need the development of regional policies to address these issues at the local level.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Aguirre, A. Alonso", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Animals", "Animals, Domestic", "Animals, Wild", "Biodiversity", "Ecology", "Humans", "Zoonoses", "Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/079785c35cb86c0a78fbe0ba8ee3cf04", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/06e64ee1da862e2338a05ec9cd71c3a3d0f7cc1d8ce2ecf2d899b0be83daed29", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/ZKL27X96", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/ZKL27X96", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/525e7268fdc5b5e006beabd6cf06af68!/b50589-53164", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "3", "pages": "315-318", "title": "ILAR journal", "volume": "58"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/079785c35cb86c0a78fbe0ba8ee3cf04"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:ZKL27X96"}, {"identifier": "10.1093/ilar/ilx035"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosyslit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid